description_text:
If you have a claw attack (either from an actual natural weapon or from an effect such as
claws of the beast
), you can use this power to improve that weapon. One of your claws becomes two-dimensional, making it razorsharp. The weapon is now psionically keen, increasing its threat range from 20 to 19–20. This benefit does not stack with other effects that improve a weapon’s threat range.
